original_title: How to Have a Moneymaking Garage Sale
overview: Learn today's simple, step-by-step way to make more money with less effort...and have fun!  Phyllis Diller shares her "garage sale secrets" with you, digging into closets, plowing through old boxes and clearing out the attic as she organizes an attractive, moneymaking garage sale.
tagline: There's gold in the old... so turn your trash into cash!
title: How to Have a Moneymaking Garage Sale
